name: Peña del cuervo
description:
Another piece from my traveling series.

Mictlantecutli( Aztec god of the dead, usually portrayed with a skull face) rising from the underworld to show us the myth of death. Hope it finds you doing what you feel passionate about and not building a stranger's dream, giving you a square planned life.

You only die once, so deliver a quality life, an authentic one, dasein.

October 2017.
